---
layout: base.njk
title: Resources and publications
eyebrow: Resources and publications
heading: Shared <em>knowledge</em>
lead: News, publications and outreach materials on the health and welfare of camelids.
description: "News, publications and outreach materials on the health and welfare of camelids by Camelid Research Studies APS."
permalink: /en/risorse/
---
<section class="bg-soft">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">News</div>
    <h2>Latest <em>news</em></h2>
    {% set articoli = collections.news | reverse %}
    {% if articoli | length %}
    <p class="empty-note" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">Our news articles are currently published in Italian.</p>
    <div class="rows">
      {% for a in articoli %}
      <a class="row" href="{{ a.url }}">
        <span class="meta">{{ a.date | dataIt }}</span>
        <span class="title">{{ a.data.title }}{% if a.data.sommario %}<small>{{ a.data.sommario }}</small>{% endif %}</span>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="empty-note">No news has been published yet. The first updates will come with the launch of the 2026&ndash;2027 projects.</div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Publications and materials</div>
    <h2>Outreach <em>materials</em></h2>
    <div class="empty-note">The association is newly established: the first publications and outreach materials will arrive with the launch of the 2026&ndash;2027 projects. Below is an example of how they will appear (placeholder content).</div>
    <div class="rows">
      {% set esempi = [
        {meta:"Publication", title:"Title of the article or study", sub:"Authors · Journal or conference · Year"},
        {meta:"Material", title:"Outreach guide on camelid welfare", sub:"Downloadable PDF"},
        {meta:"Webinar", title:"Recording of a training session", sub:"Video · Duration"}
      ] %}
      {% for r in esempi %}
      <a class="row" href="#">
        <span class="meta">{{ r.meta }}</span>
        <span class="title">{{ r.title }}<small>{{ r.sub }}</small></span>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-soft">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Coming soon</div>
    <h2>Camelid Research <em>Library</em></h2>
    <p class="lead">A scientific library of camelid research cards &mdash; summaries of studies, protocols and guidelines, searchable and filterable. In development.</p>
  </div>
</section>
